## File and Directory Naming

| What | Convention | Examples |
|---|---|---|
| All source files | kebab-case | `asset-categories.ts`, `physical-count.svelte` |
| Drizzle schema files | `<table-name>.ts` in `src/db/schema/` | `assets.ts`, `coa-findings.ts` |
| TypeBox schema files | `<table-name>.typebox.ts` in `src/db/typebox/` | `assets.typebox.ts` |
| Seed files | `<entity>.seed.ts` in `src/db/seed/` | `departments.seed.ts` |
| Test files | `<name>.test.ts` | `assets.test.ts`, `rbac.test.ts` |
| SvelteKit route files | SvelteKit convention | `+page.svelte`, `+server.ts`, `+layout.svelte` |
| API route groups | kebab-case directories | `src/api/assets/`, `src/api/coa-findings/` |
| Reusable components | PascalCase `.svelte` | `AssetCard.svelte`, `DepartmentSelector.svelte` |
| Utility files | kebab-case | `id.ts`, `date-utils.ts`, `format-currency.ts` |

